divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my back patio area smoking a cigarette, noticed two star light objects off of neighbors Windows. Was moving one on top of other. Absolutely no sound. It lasted only a few seconds. Soild star like appearance. Leaving a gliter tail. Lasted only a few seconds at most. Moved too see directly too see objects as it was too my back . But objects was gone . It had complete silence. Objects were traving too the S.w. direction. One object was moving in tandom with other only a meter apart from lower object and 1 and a half to 4 feet to rear of the lower object. Thought it looked like airplane lights on wingtips. But, was not flashing at all. I am at a compelte loss to what it could be. Let alone where it went.
